而快速的机器打造成了如此纤细的机身。唯一真正的缺点是 Air 对可负担性的关注意味着您将获得 60Hz 的显示屏，而不是新 Pro 的 120Hz。</p><p> – 丹·库珀</p><p></p><p><em>The Morning After 不仅仅是一份</em><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/about/newsletter/"><em>时事通讯</em></a><em>——它还是一个每日播客。</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-08-01-engadget-podcasts.html"><em>在这里订阅</em></a><em>，获取周一至周五的每日音频简报</em><em>。</em></p><p></p><h3>你可能错过的最重要的故事</h3><h3></h3><p><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ftc-expected-to-file-injunction-to-block-microsofts-purchase-of-activision-blizzard-165738788.html">FTC 申请禁令，阻止微软收购动视暴雪</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/former-samsung-executive-accused-of-trying-to-copy-an-entire-chip-plant-in-china-121008690.html">三星前高管被控试图复制中国的整个芯片工厂</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsofts-pc-game-pass-is-coming-to-nvidias-rival-geforce-now-service-091754446.html">微软的 PC Game Pass 即将登陆 NVIDIA 的竞争对手 GeForce Now 服务</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsungs-49-inch-curved-oled-gaming-display-is-2200-130009839.html">三星 49 英寸曲面 OLED 游戏显示器售价 2200 美元</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/immortals-of-aveum-first-look-a-little-more-magic-and-this-might-be-wonderful-133034089.html">&#39;Immortals of Aveum&#39; 第一眼：多一点魔法，这可能很棒</a></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/skull-and-bones-is-still-alive-will-apparently-have-a-closed-beta-in-august-175747813.html">&#39;Skull and Bones&#39; 仍然以某种方式仍然存在并且显然将在 8 月进行内测</a></p><p></p><h2><a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/reddit-sees-more-than-6000-communities-go-dark-in-protest-over-api-changes-095311637.html">Reddit 看到超过 6,000 个社区因 API 更改而陷入黑暗</a></h2><h3><a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/reddit-suffers-a-major-outage-after-thousands-of-subreddits-temporarily-shut-down-151741809.html">抗议活动导致网站暂时中断。</a></h3><p></p><p>如果 Reddit 首席执行官史蒂夫霍夫曼上周晚些时候的 AMA 旨在缓和公司领导层与其用户之间的紧张关系，那么它并不是很成功。 <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/reddit-sees-more-than-6000-communities-go-dark-in-protest-over-api-changes-095311637.html">超过 6,000 个 subreddit</a>现已关闭，以抗议该服务的 API 更改已将多个第三方应用程序屏蔽掉。这包括它的几个最大的社区，所有这些社区一下子变暗就足以<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/reddit-suffers-a-major-outage-after-thousands-of-subreddits-temporarily-shut-down-151741809.html">暂时推翻该网站</a>。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/reddit-sees-more-than-6000-communities-go-dark-in-protest-over-api-changes-095311637.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-mac-studio-review-m2-ultra-2023-170007838.html">Apple Mac Studio 评测（M2 Ultra，2023 年）：更适合专业人士的 Mac</a></h2><h3>现在谁需要 Mac Pro？</h3><figure> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-mac-studio-review-m2-ultra-2023-170007838.html"><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/9a715b90-09cd-11ee-bfff-c43a8141f031" style="height:410px;width:625px;" alt="桌子上的 Apple Mac Studio (2023) 图片，背景是 Apple 显示器。" data-uuid="7366cdaa-8f80-31cd-ab19-dea2593ed5bf"></a><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-mac-studio-review-m2-ultra-2023-170007838.html">Devindra Hardawar / Engadget</a></div></figure><p>阅读 Devindra Hardawar <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-mac-studio-review-m2-ultra-2023-170007838.html">对 M2 Mac Studio 的评论</a>让我想知道为什么 Mac Pro 仍然存在。当然，可扩展 RAM 和免费 PCI-E 插槽对于某些用例仍然有价值，但对于其他所有情况呢？这台微型机器发出原始的咕噜声，如果你对它进行足够的配置，即使是最强大的专业电脑也会发出咕噜咕噜的声音。继续阅读以了解这件事的速度有多快，以及是否值得投资。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-mac-studio-review-m2-ultra-2023-170007838.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/first-star-wars-outlaws-gameplay-trailer-offers-10-minutes-of-scoundrel-wish-fulfi